text: Two Flags West is a 1950 American western movie directed by Robert Wise and starring Cornel Wilde, Joseph Cotten, Linda Darnell, Jeff Chandler, Dale Robertson. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1950 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Robert Wise
